title: "bounded-loops"
abstract: "Runnable, bounded AI-agent loops: an independent gate verifies every lap under nine enforced safety bounds plus a kill switch, so a loop is DONE only when the gate says so — never when the agent claims it. Includes 68 loop folders across a dozen industries, 64 keyless out of the box."
